source: TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_SEQ_00<tab>Moxia would have you see to some foul inhabitants of the forest.
target: TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_SEQ_00<tab>Quand les Dénaturés cesseront-ils d'empoisonner l'air de la Sylve<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_SEQ_01<tab>The malicious sylphs have been planting banestools in the vicinity of the Hanging Barbs, threatening the well-being of all who reside in the surrounding environs. Slay two of the formidable fungi.
target: TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_SEQ_01<tab>Il ne sera pas dit que Moxia laissera les Dénaturés polluer l'air de la forêt sans réagir. Il vous a demandé d'aller éliminer deux <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF2090C0302 /var> aux Piques pendues.

source: TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_SEQ_02<tab>The banestools have been dealt with. Inform Moxia that she has two less fungi to fear.
target: TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez vaincu les <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF2090C0302 /var>. Retournez faire votre rapport à Moxia au Refuge.

source: TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_SEQ_03<tab>While grateful for your efforts, Moxia still continues to lament the plight of her people. It is a sad reality that the touched sylphs' mad desire for power has blinded them to the fact that they are slowly destroying their own home.
target: TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_SEQ_03<tab>Moxia est rasséréné de savoir que vous avez réussi, mais il ne décolère pas devant l'in<var 16 /var>cons<var 16 /var>cien<var 16 /var>ce des Dénaturés.
TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_TODO_01<tab>Faire un rapport à Moxia au Refuge

source: TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_MOXIA_000_000<tab>This one takes one's eyes off touched ones for one moment, and what do touched ones do? Plant stinky ones all over the Hanging Barbs!
target:
TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_MOXIA_000_000Les Dénaturés sont des aliénés, des fous!
Des champignons horribles, ils ont planté partout!

source: TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_MOXIA_000_001<tab>Trusted one knows stinky ones, yes? Stinky ones bite and gnash, and spit sickening spores to boot. Nasty things, those ones are.
target:
TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_MOXIA_000_001Les exhalaisons des sont nocives,
elles corrompent l'air de la Sylve.

source: TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_MOXIA_000_002<tab>What's more, touched ones have trained stinky ones to attack walking ones on sight! Is there no end to those ones' mischief?
target:
TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_MOXIA_000_002Va aux Piques pendues, je t'en supplie,
et réduis-les en bouillie!

source: TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_MOXIA_000_003<tab>No, these ones are not safe with stinky ones lurking about. Will trusted one squash stinky ones so that these ones can play in the Barbs again?
target:
TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_MOXIA_000_003Mais sois quand même prudent,
les Dénaturés leur lancent souvent des sorts,
pour ,
et pour les rendre plus forts.

source: TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_MOXIA_000_004<tab>Stinky ones are no match for trusted one. This one knows.
target:
TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_MOXIA_000_004C'est pour ça que nous ne pouvons pas les affronter,
tu es la seule personne qui peut nous aider.

source: TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_MOXIA_000_010<tab>Trusted one will squash stinky ones so that these ones can frolic in the Barbs again, yes? Be careful, stinky ones have been trained by touched ones to attack walking ones on sight.
target:
TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_MOXIA_000_010Va aux Piques pendues, je t'en supplie,
et réduis les en bouillie!

source: TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_MOXIA_000_020<tab>This one is glad to see trusted one safe!
target:
TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_MOXIA_000_020Tu nous reviens en vie,
et tu as vaincu ces ignobles fungi!

source: TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_MOXIA_000_021<tab>Stinky ones are no more? This one knew that trusted one could be trusted, tee hee!
target:
TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_MOXIA_000_021Nous allons pouvoir à nouveau respirer,
au sens propre, comme au sens figuré.

source: TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_MOXIA_000_022<tab>This one knows not what touched ones are thinking. Touched ones destroy the forest for every one, including ones' selves.
target:
TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_MOXIA_000_022Quant aux Dénaturés, ne réfléchissent-ils jamais?
Que s'imaginent-ils qu'il va se passer?

source: TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_MOXIA_000_023<tab>This one tried to say so, but this one's words do not reach those ones. Are those ones truly lost...?
target:
TEXT_BANSYL310_01286_MOXIA_000_023C'est leur propre habitat qu'ils mettent en péril!
Ne penser qu'à son plaisir, voilà qui est puéril.
